  "description": "<p>AKA Fantastic Illicit Substances and How to Use Them<br /><br />This module aims to add illicit substances and paraphernalia to your DND games. Split into Fantasy, Sci-Fi, and Modern options. Includes Macros and Journal entries. You can easily create and codify your own substances and paraphernalia.<br /><br />Features<br />- Drugs (3 categories, Stimulant, Mind-Altering, and Performance-Enhancing, actual names of categories TBD)<br />- Drug related accessories<br />- Drugs add active effects<br />- Drugs can have required paraphernalia, which means they can't be consumed without the right gear, or the right range of gear<br />- If you have Dynamic Active Effects (DAE), Midi-QoL, Times Up, and Token Magic Effects, expanded automation and effects apply/can be addded</p>",
